column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name], so.bestobjid, so.ra, so.dec, so.plate, so.mjd, so.fiberID, gsl.oiii_#_flux, gsl.h_beta_flux, gsl.nii_#_flux, gsl.h_alpha_flux, so.z, so.snMedian_g FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN SpecObjAll so ON so.specObjID = x.specObjID JOIN GalSpecLine as gsl ON so.specObjid = gsl.specObjid
